---
title: Prime Rib and Grilled Onion Burger with Secret Sauce and Grilled Potatoes
description: American drive-thru-style burgers in Canada! Better yet, out of the drive-thru and onto the grill! "Secret sauce" is delicious spread on toasted buns and as a dip for grilled potatoes! Foil-pouch onions add lusciousness to this burger.
